Usage: saveModel [-help] -dir <string> [-ilm] [-sdf] [-spef] [-stream [-mapFile <string>] [-outputMacros ]]

-help                  # Prints out the command usage
-dir <string>          # <Output directory name> (string, required)
-ilm                   # <Generate Interface Logic Model (ILM)>
                       # (bool, optional)
-mapFile <string>      # <Output directory name> (string, optional)
-outputMacros          # <Generate stream data> (bool, optional)
-sdf                   # <Generate Delay model (SDF)> (bool, optional)
-spef                  # <Generate Parasitic model (SPEF)> (bool, optional)
-stream                # <Generate stream data> (bool, optional)